Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:19.44,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:25.26,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,a thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:31.01,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:37.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,the Light struck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:43.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:49.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:53.13,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:58.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\Nas the war rages on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:01.49,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:06.86,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:12.88,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:18.37,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:24.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:39.53,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Both "Shao Pai Long," the fantasy kung-fu\Nmovie made aboard the Macross,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.11,0:01:44.01,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and footage from the collapse of\Nthe Omni-Directional Barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:47.47,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,have been sent to the Zentradi's\Nmain Bodol fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:52.94,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing these things sends\Na shock through Bodolzaa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:01.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shao Pai Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:04.69,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shao Pai Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:11.74,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To save a diseased city, he has returned
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:16.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the miclones?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:20.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Evil's slayer! Slayer! Slayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:34.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And they possess weapons this powerful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:39.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:42.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is true, they are beings to be feared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:47.71,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(89,138)}LOVE CONCERT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:53.37,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zero-g love, zero-g love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:56.75,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zero-g love, zero-g love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:03:02.77,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With him after school, on my way home
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:09.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the corner of that same old intersection
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:07.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is called "song"?\NIt feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:11.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But is it true that the real one\Nis aboard the Macross?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:14.43,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He made sure no one else was around
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:12.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:16.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And watching the real one sing in person\Nmakes you feel even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, "song" sure is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:20.98,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then without warning, he kissed me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:26.71,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I was so angry, I led him to think,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:24.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?\NYou're gonna break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.59,0:03:26.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:30.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you push this down,\Nit will play another song.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:31.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,ANOTHER song?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean there's more than one song?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:36.51,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:40.90,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:44.62,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shining, making a rapid descent
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:45.89,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then BOOM! he...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Song"?\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:51.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you listen to it, it makes\Nyou feel really great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:53.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt so good before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:55.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Warera Nantes has it.\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A disturbance aboard Britai's ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:14.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, those three spies he\Nsent aboard the Macross
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:16.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,brought a bunch of strange\Nthings back with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:19.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's causing a lot of commotion\Namong the men.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:21.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's all this is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:28.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of these guys are saying they'd like\Nto surrender and live on the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:30.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender?\NTo the enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:33.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not just one or two of them either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:34.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:37.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not tolerate talk of surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they saying this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:40.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know really know\Nthe details...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:43.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do our superiors know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:44.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:48.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This damn Macross!\NIt's gotten everybody running scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I'll have to destroy\Nthe Macross myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A miclone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:02.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You want us to capture a miclone, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:06.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have reviewed all the materials\Nyou sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:08.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,My order is in response to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:13.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost certain that these people\Nare the Protoculture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:17.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That means they pose an\Nextreme danger to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:22.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You must capture a miclone and\Nonce again study it in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Once this is complete, we will\Nmove to the final stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:26.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Final stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What would that be, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:34.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact with beings who possess culture has\Nalways had a negative effect on our soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:40.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,To avoid that, we must gather all the data\Nwe can and then annihilate the miclones!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:42.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, sir.\NWe will capture a miclone at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:52.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,On the Macross, a girl the size of this photo\Nlets other miclones listen to her songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:53.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:55.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:01.43,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,We are about to attack the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:04.50,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,All personnel, report to your battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:08.81,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat, we are about to attack the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:10.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to attack the Macross?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:15.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do we do?!\NIf we attack the Macross, we'll kill this girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:17.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't get to hear her songs anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:21.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just songs.\NThey have all sorts of things that we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:24.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And all of it will be gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:36.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's surrender!\NWe can surrender and live on that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:37.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:40.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we try thinking this through,\Nwe'll never do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:44.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,During the attack, if we see a chance to\Nrun to the Macross, we take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:45.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:46.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:49.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're discovered, they'll\Nexecute us for desertion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll worry about that once it actually happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:56.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me with you!\NTo the Macross, and all the stuff we don't have!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:57.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:06:59.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:00.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:02.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we'll all go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:05.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But first we'll have to become miclones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:08.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys know how to work that machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:09.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:10.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.\NSomeone in this group knows how.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:18.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Torakajiide!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:21.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:24.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I operate the machinery without\Nauthorization, I'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:27.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're discovered,\Nwe'll all be facing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:29.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to hear a real song, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:35.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then help us!\NI'll give you this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:37.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And the doll and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:39.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:44.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a whole lot of culture\Nthat'll make you feel good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:48.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's not the only woman\Nthere, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:11.59,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:16.54,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that's here\Nis a meaningless war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:38.20,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:42.75,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:46.49,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shining, making a rapid descent
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:50.16,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then BOOM! he makes a sudden climb
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:49.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:55.86,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leaving a long trail of vapor
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:09:02.12,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He traces two big hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:09.37,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A love sign in the big, blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:12.90,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I love you, you love me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:17.39,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he's head over heels
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:23.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For his plane instead of me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:24.04,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:27.29,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:27.03,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,I can fight to protect Minmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:33.99,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:30.35,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough. That's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:34.05,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't get away from here, then\Nfighting for her sake is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:49.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:53.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, I'll sing "Love Drifts Away."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:55.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:05.56,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:08.02,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks especially lovely today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:13.62,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Time drifts away,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:18.91,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}love drifts away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:30.36,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Standing before me, a sad look on your face,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:30.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be nice if the enemy doesn't\Ncome today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:41.87,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know you're going off to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:34.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to feel a passionate love\Nlike in the song too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:36.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:38.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:53.34,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the men, together, as if possessed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:59.74,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With mouths pulled tight, with eyes burning,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:05.52,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They march in step.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:16.71,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I'll be left behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:15.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be thinking about Major Focker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This song must be really hard on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:22.70,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All for war,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:22.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She acts happy, but you can't forget\Na love like that so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:23.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:27.68,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All for pride
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:34.12,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Time drifts away,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:39.78,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}love drifts away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:51.56,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I rot away...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:10.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,L-O-V-E! Lovely Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:13.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,L-O-V-E!\NLovely Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:17.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,L-O-V-E! Lovely Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:20.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,L-O-V-E!\NLovely Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:48.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We lure them into launching a\NDaedalus Attack on our ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:49.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:54.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little crude, but if we use their\NDaedalus Attack against them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:58.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,we should be able to insert a Reguld\Nsquadron aboard their ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:03.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can capture not just a miclone,\Nbut the Macross itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:06.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They pierce our flesh but we\Nbreak their bones, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:11.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely. However, we cannot let them\Nchoose which area to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:15.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one section will\Ndo: the ship's bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:21.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with the bow ruptured, we will be able\Nto hold out for 4 or even 5 {\i1}adenors{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:23.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:27.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was developed by analyzing data\Nbrought back by our spies
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:30.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,regarding the Macross's attack patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:31.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:41.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,None of us were discovered.\NOur plan's a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:43.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too soon to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:47.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we see our chance,\Nwe lie low and keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:58.22,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,All Reguld and Noujadeul-Ger forces:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:00.77,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Move to the ship's bow at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:04.25,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Once in position, stand by for further orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:06.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The bow?\NThat's not what we usually do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:07.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:11.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic.\NWe know we're attacking the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:14.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our chance will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:20.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, men! Your orders are when the\NMacross closes and launches its fighters,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,we attack them in waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:23.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:27.91,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,And with permission from above.\NWell, it's my pleasure to serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Number of ships is approximately thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're headed straight for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:44.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a fraction of their main force.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:48.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And we can't expect any help\Nfrom our own forces, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:51.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't let them destroy us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:53.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Send the order to scramble\NValkyrie squadrons!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:54.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:07.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy fighters have been deployed and\Nare closing in from 12 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:08.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:12.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not acting normally.\NBe careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:14.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to remind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:16.58,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay, I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:29.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:52.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So far, they've kept to the\Nusual pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is tactical leader Grundkol.\NAll units are in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.61,0:15:59.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, head toward the Macross.\NThis ship will take the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:01.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:04.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Remind the other ships that our objective\Nis to capture the Macross,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:07.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and that this ship will be\Ndamaged in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:07.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:20.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Their fleet's up to something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:34.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:38.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lure them in as close as possible,\Nthen launch a Daedalus Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:42.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,To save the Macross, we'll have to take\Nthem out one ship at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:43.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:46.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to launch a\NDaedalus Attack on my mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:47.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:56.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that just now?\NOur mission is to storm the Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:58.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's our chance!\NWhat luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:01.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to get inside and\Nthen we've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:05.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Or if we get inside and our luck\Nruns out, we all die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just lie low for as long as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:10.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I'll tell the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:25.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay, keep going!\NKeep singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:26.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:29.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, the concert will continue as planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:30.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:33.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let this barbaric war\Nget the better of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:36.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Singing mustn't be defeated by\Nweapons of destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:39.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, everyone!\NLet's keep this concert going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:43.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sing, Minmay!\NSing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:45.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sing as loud as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:47.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:48.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, be brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:54.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:58.83,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoosh, whoosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:00.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Louder than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:03.65,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:07.79,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:11.95,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shining, making a rapid descent
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:13.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!\NThat's the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:15.89,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then BOOM! he makes a sudden climb
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:21.41,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leaving a long trail of vapor
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:27.56,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He traces two big hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:34.59,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A love sign in the big, blue sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:41.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! That large ship is\Nheaded straight for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:43.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They want to ram us?!\NEvasive maneuvers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:46.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good!\NThe surrounding ships have blocked us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:48.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Execute Daedalus Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:53.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Target the large ship and open up\Nan escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:56.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!\NDaedalus Attack, stand by!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:22.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:26.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:48.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:49.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:51.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle pods have broken in through\Nthe starboard side!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been boarded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There!\NRun this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:17.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle pods have broken in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:20.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,50 or 60 of them are shooting up\Nthe interior right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:21.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Return at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the concert hall okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:26.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We still don't have any details.\NLieutenant Ichijo, just hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:29.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max, battle pods have\Nboarded the Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:31.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:32.98,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:38.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:48.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten battle pods sighted\Non Suzuran Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:49.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We are exchanging gunfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:50.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Defense forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:52.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy has destroyed an\Nentire section of the base!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:53.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}We are now at 10th Street
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:55.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}in front of the base gate!\NWe have engaged the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:20:57.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Please send a Destroid platoon at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.66,0:21:00.76,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be at the concert hall too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:03.94,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo, please save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:05.59,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:10.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dancing in the sky, the silver wings
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:12.57,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shao Pai Long...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:15.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}"Shao Pai Long!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:17.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sing for the audience!\NSing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}"Remember!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:23.12,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The eyes of fire splitting the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:25.20,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shao Pai Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sing louder!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:28.20,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Shao Pai Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:28.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shao Pai Long!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:33.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:50.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaifun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:51.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.82,0:22:20.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:24.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.16,0:22:42.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it:\Nit's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:48.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt?\NHere...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.57,0:23:07.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so sweaty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:29.50,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.41,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(72,107)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.41,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(298,455)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:41.37,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The Zentradi infiltration of the Macross\Nhas allowed the three spies
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.63,0:23:44.00,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and other defectors\Nto board the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:47.39,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Troubled by the request for asylum\Nfrom these 23 deserters,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.43,0:23:51.33,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Global decides to summon those who\Nhave had contact with the Zentradi:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.61,0:23:54.29,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,namely, Hikaru, Misa, and Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.26,0:23:58.44,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.85,0:24:01.95,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"DROP OUT"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.44,0:24:02.45,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(68,145)}DROP OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.59,0:24:23.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.52,0:24:29.89,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.18,0:24:36.54,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running to the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.75,0:24:44.20,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.56,0:24:51.00,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.29,0:24:56.78,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.12,0:25:04.36,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.71,0:25:15.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
